parameters: \n<Pierrot>Everyone, today Eury-chan will be joining us in the game.

\n<Pierrot>The rules are simple. Gentlemen, please hide behind the door
of your choice.

\n<Pierrot>When Eury-chan comes in, you can have your way with her
once, and that's okay.

\n<Pierrot>Eury-chan can be taken advantage of multiple times, but as
long as she can stand and reach the goal, she clears the
game.

\n<Memory Assistance Demon>"It seems that no matter which door you choose in this game,
the outcome is the same. By the way, shall we return to the
memory room?"
\n<Mister>You still have such a huggable body!

\n<Pierrot>Looks like you got fucked once. Can you still stand and
walk?
\n<Pierrot>Then, keep up the good work with the rest.
\n<Pierrot>"The right path must be the correct one, surely."
\n<Mister>You still have such a huggable body!

\n<Pierrot>Looks like you've been taken once. Can you still stand and
walk?
